{"data": [{"id": "4742704", "title": "FitLife Brands: Q3 Results Weren't As Bad As They Seem - Still A Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/619091536/image_619091536.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Scoop of whey protein on black background. Chocolate flawour\" data-id=\"619091536\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1017px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/619091536/image_619091536.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/619091536/image_619091536.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/619091536/image_619091536.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/619091536/image_619091536.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/619091536/image_619091536.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/619091536/image_619091536.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/619091536/image_619091536.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/619091536/image_619091536.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Chet_W/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment thesis</h2> <p>I previously <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4722779-fitlife-brands-market-consolidator-ceo-with-value-investing-background\">covered FitLife Brands, Inc.</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/FTLF\" title=\"FitLife Brands, Inc.\">FTLF</a></span>) and shared the story behind it, its CEO, and the path to future growth. Since then, the stock has barely moved, but in between, the Q3 2024 results were presented, in</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/619091536/image_619091536.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742704-fitlife-brands-q3-results-werent-as-bad-as-they-seem-still-a-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 23:29:30"}, {"id": "4742702", "title": "Why Micron Could Double Its Valuation", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2083023800/image_2083023800.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"High bandwidth Memory concepts backgrounds. 3d rendering\" data-id=\"2083023800\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2083023800/image_2083023800.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2083023800/image_2083023800.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2083023800/image_2083023800.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2083023800/image_2083023800.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2083023800/image_2083023800.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2083023800/image_2083023800.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2083023800/image_2083023800.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2083023800/image_2083023800.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">mesh cube</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Micron (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MU\" title=\"Micron Technology, Inc.\">MU</a></span>) is scheduled to submit its first fiscal quarter earnings sheet on December 18, 2024 and I believe the memory maker has a strong chance to beat earnings estimates as well as impress investors with its</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2083023800/image_2083023800.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742702-why-micron-could-double-its-valuation", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 23:05:04"}, {"id": "4742705", "title": "Is Market Optimism Outpacing Realistic Growth Potential?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397937755/image_1397937755.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Financial asset invest analysis with volume and candle stick chart\" data-id=\"1397937755\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397937755/image_1397937755.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397937755/image_1397937755.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397937755/image_1397937755.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397937755/image_1397937755.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397937755/image_1397937755.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397937755/image_1397937755.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397937755/image_1397937755.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397937755/image_1397937755.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">TERADAT SANTIVIVUT</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Equity markets have spent much of 2024 in record territory. But with a new U.S. president moving into the White House, concerns about current valuations and potential economic headwinds, can that momentum continue? Phil Davis, founder of Philstockworld.com, discusses why he believes recent market</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397937755/image_1397937755.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742705-market-optimism-outpacing-realistic-growth-potential", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 22:46:00"}, {"id": "4742703", "title": "EUR/USD: Additional Accommodative Monetary Policy Guidance From The ECB May Be Forthcoming", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1126632524/image_1126632524.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Euro currency symbol\" data-id=\"1126632524\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"7952px\" height=\"5304px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1126632524/image_1126632524.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1126632524/image_1126632524.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1126632524/image_1126632524.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1126632524/image_1126632524.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1126632524/image_1126632524.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1126632524/image_1126632524.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1126632524/image_1126632524.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1126632524/image_1126632524.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Daniel Grizelj</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Kelvin Wong</em></p> <p>For next Thursday, 12 December European Central Bank (ECB) monetary policy outcome, market participants are likely to expect a 25-basis point (BPS) cut rather than a more aggressive reduction of 50 bps based on short-term interest rate futures pricing.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1126632524/image_1126632524.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742703-eur-usd-additional-accommodative-monetary-policy-guidance-ecb-may-be-forthcoming", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 22:23:00"}, {"id": "4742701", "title": "GraniteShares 2x Long COIN ETF: Fortune Favors The Brave", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383032511/image_1383032511.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Paying in cyber space\" data-id=\"1383032511\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1266px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383032511/image_1383032511.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383032511/image_1383032511.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383032511/image_1383032511.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383032511/image_1383032511.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383032511/image_1383032511.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383032511/image_1383032511.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383032511/image_1383032511.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383032511/image_1383032511.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I last covered the <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4717407-graniteshares-2x-long-coin-etf-proof-in-pudding\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4717407-graniteshares-2x-long-coin-etf-proof-in-pudding\" target=\"_blank\">GraniteShares 2x Long COIN Daily ETF</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CONL\" title=\"GraniteShares 2x Long COIN Daily ETF\">CONL</a></span>) for Seeking Alpha in late August. For the second time this year, I rated CONL a 'sell' and made the argument that the proof was in the pudding on the fund. At</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383032511/image_1383032511.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742701-graniteshares-2x-long-coin-etf-fortune-favors-the-brave", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 22:19:26"}, {"id": "4742699", "title": "Zumiez Is Recovering, But The Price Already Discounts A Full Turnaround", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Skateboarder falling off of railing in skate park\" data-id=\"516750419\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Thomas Barwick/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Zumiez Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ZUMZ\" title=\"Zumiez Inc.\">ZUMZ</a></span>) reported a <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4368139-zumiez-gaap-eps-of-0_06-beats-0_03-revenue-of-222_48m-beats-0_44m\">great 3Q24</a>, with comparables up 7.5% (up from Q2 and Q1), and guiding for a similar quarter in 4Q24. The company leveraged its margins despite lower absolute sales (calendar shift).</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742699-zumiez-is-recovering-but-the-price-already-discounts-a-full-turnaround", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 22:13:22"}, {"id": "4742696", "title": "Droning On About Defense: Why AeroVironment Is A Weapon Of Choice", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A flying drone\" data-id=\"956306692\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6674px\" height=\"5338px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Yagi Studio</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p><em>\u201cIdiots.\u201d</em></p> <p>That's what Elon Musk called the producers of the F-35, the fighter jet program led by Lockheed Martin (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LMT\" title=\"Lockheed Martin Corporation\">LMT</a>).</p> <p>According to <a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/elon-musk-f35-idiots-building-unmanned-jets-drone-warfare-doge-2024-11?international=true&amp;r=US&amp;IR=T\" rel=\"nofollow\">Business Insider</a>, Elon Musk tweeted <em>\u201cMeanwhile, some idiots are still building manned fighter jets</em></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742696-droning-on-about-defense-why-aerovironment-is-a-weapon-of-choice", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 22:02:51"}, {"id": "4742694", "title": "Zoetis: Are Competition And Price Increases A Cause For Concern?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155002603/image_2155002603.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Fluffy little dog getting a haircut at pet groomer\" data-id=\"2155002603\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155002603/image_2155002603.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155002603/image_2155002603.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155002603/image_2155002603.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155002603/image_2155002603.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155002603/image_2155002603.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155002603/image_2155002603.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155002603/image_2155002603.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.see